          </p>

          <div class="flex justify-between pt-4 border-t border-slate-100 mt-4">
            <button class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold"
                    data-go-module="5">
              ‚Üê Volver al M√≥dulo 2
            </button>
